      <div type="transcription" xml:id="transcription_aad_0107" xml:lang="en">
        <div type="letter">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00355/" ed="1r" type="sheet"/>
          <div type="letter_message" hand="#hand_blue_auden">
            <opener hand="#print_black_auden">
              <dateline>
                <seg hand="#hand_blue_auden">
                  <date>
                    <lb/>May 3<hi rend="superscript">rd<unclear>.</unclear></hi>
                  </date>
                </seg>
                <placeName>
                  <address xml:lang="de">
                    <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_2">KIRCHSTETTEN (WESTBAHN)
                    <lb/>HINTERHOLZ 6
                    <lb/>N.-Ö., <foreign xml:lang="en">AUSTRIA</foreign></rs>
                  </address>
                </placeName>
                <persName>
                  <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">W. H. AUDEN</rs>
                </persName>
              </dateline>
              <salute hand="#hand_blue_auden">
                <lb/>Dear <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_137">D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Kraus</rs>:
              </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
              <lb/>Yo<unclear>u</unclear> letter of Ma<unclear>r</unclear>ch 28<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> was forwarded <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">to
              <lb/>me in New York</rs>,j<unclear>u</unclear>st missed, and only
              <lb/>got <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_2">here</rs> again yesterday.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>I gre<unclear>a</unclear>tly apprecia<unclear>te</unclear> the honor of your
              <lb/>invitati<unclear>n</unclear> to attend the <rs type="event" ref="#amp_event_id_31"><unclear>c</unclear>onference on <hi rend="underline" hand="#hand_blue_auden">literatu</hi>re:
              <lb/><hi rend="underline" hand="#hand_blue_auden">tradition and revolutio<unclear>r</unclear></hi></rs> , <del rend="overstrike" hand="#hand_blue_auden"><unclear>in</unclear></del> next October.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>Unfortu<unclear>na</unclear>tely, I have <rs type="event" ref="#amp_event_id_30" cert="medium">engagements in
              <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_239">E<unclear>n</unclear>gland</rs> at that time</rs>, so cannot a<unclear>c</unclear>cept.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>Thank you very mu<unclear>c</unclear>h for <unclear>as</unclear>king me.
            </p>
            <closer>
              <salute>
                <lb/>yours since<unclear>re</unclear>ly
              </salute>
              <signed>
                <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">W<unclear>.</unclear>H<unclear>.</unclear>Auden</rs>
              </signed>
            </closer>
          </div>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00356/" ed="1v" type="sheet"/>
        </div>
      </div>
